{"word":"βάσκω","slug":"βάσκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βάσκω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>akin to <a href='S:βαίνω'><el>βαίνω</el></a>, <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>χάσκω, χαίνω</el>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only used in <a href='S:imperative mood'>imperat.</a> \n<p/><el>βάσκ' ἴθι</el> <i>speed thee! away!</i> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; also <i>come!</i> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/>"}]}